sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant Activator as Knative Activator /<br/>Queue Proxy<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant Caikit as Caikit transformer-container<br/>8080/TCP (HTTP)<br/>8085/TCP (gRPC h2c)
    participant TGIS as TGIS kserve-container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>(localhost)
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(PVC / S3)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>(openshift-user-workload-monitoring)

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Activator: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8012, mTLS<br/>Auth: Istio PeerAuthentication
    Activator->>Caikit: Forward to transformer<br/>HTTP/8080, mTLS (sidecar)<br/>Auth: Istio PeerAuthentication
    Caikit->>TGIS: Delegate inference<br/>gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>No encryption (loopback)
    TGIS->>Storage: Load model artifacts<br/>Filesystem or HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: IAM credentials
    Storage-->>TGIS: Model weights
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result (gRPC)
    Caikit-->>Activator: JSON response
    Activator-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: gRPC TextGeneration call<br/>HTTPS (h2)/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Activator: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8012, mTLS<br/>Auth: Istio PeerAuthentication
    Activator->>Caikit: Forward to transformer<br/>gRPC (h2c)/8085, mTLS (sidecar)<br/>Auth: Istio PeerAuthentication
    Caikit->>TGIS: Delegate inference<br/>gRPC/8033 (localhost)<br/>No encryption
    TGIS-->>Caikit: Inference result
    Caikit-->>Activator: gRPC response
    Activator-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Prometheus,Caikit: Flow 3: Metrics Scraping

    Prometheus->>Caikit: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8086<br/>PERMISSIVE mTLS (no cert required)
    Caikit-->>Prometheus: Caikit runtime metrics
